  "body": "Currently it seems that helm package only accepts one chart directory to package. \n\nFor example, `helm package mariadb mariadb-cluster` only packages the mariadb chart ignoring the other chart.\n\nAllowing multiple charts as input will help in case that the user wants to use bash expansion like `helm package .`\n",
